com.feilong.core.lang.thread

Class DefaultPartitionRunnableBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.feilong.core.lang.thread.DefaultPartitionRunnableBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PartitionRunnableBuilder<T>

    public class DefaultPartitionRunnableBuilder<T>
extends Object
implements PartitionRunnableBuilder<T>
    默认的 PartitionRunnableBuilder.

    重构:

    对于以下代码: 

     
 ThreadUtil.execute(list, 5, new PartitionRunnableBuilder<String>(){
 
     public Runnable build(final List<String> perBatchList,PartitionThreadEntity partitionThreadEntity,Map<String, ?> paramsMap){
 
         return new Runnable(){
 
             public void run(){
                 map.putAll(handle(perBatchList, noList));
             }
         };
     }
 });
    可以重构成: 
     ThreadUtil.execute(list, 5, new DefaultPartitionRunnableBuilder<>(new Call<String>(){
 
     public void call(List<String> perBatchList,PartitionThreadEntity partitionThreadEntity,Map<String, ?> paramsMap){
         map.putAll(handle(perBatchList, noList));
     }
 }));
    从 13 行 简写到 6 行
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    feilong
